A band of thieves appeared, and it's been several days since
the orphanage became their den.

The boy who spent sleepless nights felt a thirst one night
and slipped out of his bedchamber in the dead of night.

Eventually, his legs led him... to the bedroom of the woman
he adored.

Standing in front of the door, the boy heard a faint woman's
voice leaking from inside the room.

No doubt the thieves were subjecting the woman to their vile
acts again tonight... A flame of anger was lit in the boy's
heart.

But... something was off. The voices he heard were not of
despair.

On the contrary, the woman's voice sounded joyful, almost
gleeful.

The boy pressed his face against the keyhole, listening
intently.

Without a doubt, the woman was letting out moans. And he
could hear the men's vulgar laughter.

Amidst the sultry voices echoing through, the thieves
jovially boasted to the woman about their past deeds of
valor.

How they robbed, violated, and killed in every town and
village they visited.

The men spoke proudly and loudly of such atrocities that one
would normally want to cover their ears.

Among them was a name of a village that the boy could not
afford to miss hearing.
It was... the village where he was born.
His father had not died from an epidemic.

Now, just beyond a single door, the man who took his
father's life and the heart and body of the woman he revered
was jesting and sharing drinks with his comrades.
A

With unwavering conviction, the boy makes his way to the
bedroom of the woman he once adored.

And just like that night two years ago, he presses his ear
against the door to spy on the situation inside.

He could hear the woman's moans and a man's vulgar laughter,
sounds that had clung to his ears since the night he left
this place.

The woman, swaying her ripe breasts, straddles the man and
greedily takes his erect member into her genitals. She
indulges in pleasure, her face beaming with a full smile.

Whether she had been thoroughly trained to reach this point
was uncertain. However, it was clear that this act was no
longer one of violation.

Witnessing this scene, the boy thinks that surely this woman
will continue to live in the sexual bliss given to her by
these men.

But... if. If this scene was not what the woman desired. If
deep down she was seeking salvation.

If that were the case... then he alone could save her. She
had given him just that much.

In an instant, without hesitation, the boy bursts into the
bedroom and cuts down the man, who seemed unable to grasp
the situation, with a single stroke.

The woman, naked, stares at the boy in surprise, her mouth
moving rapidly as if to say something.

Eventually, words begin to form from the mouth of the woman,
who seemed unable to comprehend the situation.

A reunion after two years. And now, the boy who saved the
woman from being attacked by bandits.

\N<Segi>So... feeling utterly alone in the world, he eventually
heard about the Lyuda Military Training Association and came
to town relying on distant relatives.

\N<Segi>You can't qualify to participate unless you're a resident of
this town...
\N<Segi>...

\N<Segi>...I still couldn't find any convenient weaknesses after
all.
\N<Segi>But... this means...

\N<Segi>...Indeed, I couldn't find any weaknesses or
vulnerabilities. But there's one thing I'm certain of.

\N<Segi>Fubii... His combat ability is indeed not to be
underestimated. If he could take on a band of thieves all by
himself... if this is true, can I really win against such a
person?
\N<Segi>I can't stay as I am now... I have to do everything I can.
\N<Segi>And for that... I really need to go to the ruins.

\N<Segi>But even if I want to train in the ruins, there's a lock on
the door... and I don't have the knowledge to unlock it.

\N<Segi>Someone in this town who has that knowledge... or a place
that deals with tools for unlocking...

\N<Segi>...I guess I have no choice but to get something suitable
from Mr. Hojiko's place...
